rows.label: tev066401_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Ni Gombe about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Ni Gombe about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_MSG0001
rows.name:
At first, I thought naught of your kind.
What reason had I to think you special?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_MSG0002
rows.name:
But then you vanquished Goetia, and claimed victory
over Prince Jiarg himself in a duel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_MSG0003
rows.name:
You even brought down the Zu Pharg,
and Ryyz and Dagahn with it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_MSG0004
rows.name:
This human strength of yours astounds me.
The Ganglion must be quivering in their boots![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_MSG0005
rows.name:
I shall have to train harder if I am to ever stand as
tall as you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_MSG0017
rows.name:
Did you know that Gi Zang had a Prone pupil?
This was long ago, of course.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_MSG0018
rows.name:
Gi Zang says he will train me harder and teach me
all he was unable to teach his former pupil.
My aching muscles tell me he is intent on it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_MSG0019
rows.name:
But who is this brother pupil of mine?
I should like to meet him one day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_MSG0020
rows.name:
If he has been put through half as many trials as I,
this Prone must be terribly strong.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_MSG0025
rows.name:
The other day, a Prone named Sajif Scoppio told
me I was no true soldier until I had learned human
military tactics and strategies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_MSG0026
rows.name:
At first, I was taken aback by such great insult,
but then I learned that Scoppio has been evangelizing
strategy to all the warriors on this ship.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_MSG0027
rows.name:
Were these "Napoleon" and "Clausewitz" fellows
really as tremendous as he says?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066401_MSG0028
rows.name:
As the leader of the Go Rogan squadron,
perhaps I have a duty to learn their methods.[ST:wait ]
